test_large_range:
assert [] == [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, ...]
  Right contains 8 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]
  + []
test_even_range:
assert [1, 3, 5, 7, 9] == [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 4
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 14
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14, 16, 18]
  + [1, 3, 5, 7, 9]
test_zero_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, ...] == []
  Left contains 9 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]
